Net/Amazon/DVD2IMDB version 0.02
==================================

This module is designed to scrape a designated user's DVD Profiler profile and 
grab all the associated movie UPC symbols. This can be quickly tied in with the 
Net::Amazon::DVD2IMDB module to get the resulting IMDB movie information.

See the POD documentation for more info.

More information can also be found here:
    http://ejohn.org/projects/dvdprofiler/

INSTALLATION

This module requires LWP::Simple, which is part of the LWP package.

Once all dependencies have been resolved, "Net::DVDProfiler" installs 
with the typical sequence

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

